OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1782648717
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCTerrestrial TV switch-off: a
OL,4,Cheadline the government can't afford
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt argued that three national
OL,7,Fmultiplexes should be retained after
OL,8,F2034. They would switch to the
OL,9,Fcompression method currently used for
OL,10,Fthe HD multiplex.
OL,12,FThis would mean no real risk of anyone
OL,13,Flosing a PSB channel while the
OL,14,Fcompression could potentially allow for
OL,15,Fa full range of HD and SD channels `
OL,16,Fsimilar to your current mix ` on
OL,17,FFreeview.
OL,19,FAt worst the owners of a few cheaper
OL,20,Fand older sets might need a cheap set
OL,21,Ftop box.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,147,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14606
SC,0006
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1782648717
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCTerrestrial TV switch-off: a
OL,4,Cheadline the government can't afford
OL,5,
OL,6,FThis solution would also mean the end
OL,7,Fof Freeview Light ` the full range of
OL,8,FFTA channels must be available
OL,9,Feverywhere.
OL,11,FUnless the government wants more
OL,12,Fnegative headlines it can scarcely
OL,13,Fafford, it must make a few key points
OL,14,Fclear.
OL,16,F- Terrestrial television will continue
OL,17,Findefinitely ` until at least 2034.
OL,19,F- If terrestrial TV eventually accounts
OL,20,Ffor a very small proportion of viewing
OL,21,F(say less than 10pc of households) then
OL,22,Fa switch off can be considered.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,147,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14607
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F146A1782648717
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCTerrestrial TV switch-off: a
OL,4,Cheadline the government can't afford
OL,5,
OL,6,F- Any switch off would require 2 years
OL,7,Fnotice and full help to ensure nobody
OL,8,Floses out.
OL,10,FAny suggestion otherwise, speaks of
OL,11,Ftone deaf politicians who live in
OL,12,Fbubbles.
OL,14,FMeanwhile if broadcasters believe
OL,15,Finternet delivery is the future, the
OL,16,Fchallenge is to persuade the majority
OL,17,Fof us to come on that journey with them
OL,18,Fvoluntarily.
OL,20,FI'm still braced for a few more
OL,21,Fnegative stories before R4 LW finally `
OL,22,Fand belatedly ` shuts in a fortnight.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
